    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink126">
<l>kaṇṭiku mallamō koṇkaniṉ kēḷē</l>
<l>yuṇkaṇ vaṇṭiṉa moyppat</l>
<l>teṇkaṭaṟ peruntirai mūḻku vōḷē</l>
</lg>
<lg xml:lang="en">
<l>We have seen your friend, haven't we, oh man from the maritime tract?</l>
<l>She who dove into the great waves of the clear sea</l>
<l>As groups of bees crowded around her collyrium-rimmed eyes?</l>
</lg>
    </div>
